original_title: Thumb Wars IX: The Thighs of Skyskipper
overview: Thumb Wars IX is the epic tale of Loke Skyskipper and family. The story reveals the truth behind the seemingly reclusive Loke Skyskipper while tracking the ongoing internal conflict of Thumblo Ren and the mysterious origin story of Thumbray. The focus is on the fan base and ALL will be revealed.
title: Thumb Wars IX: The Thighs of Skyskipper
